race.comment: SMICHOV (7) Sydney-trained gelding with his hoof on the till. Sat on the good speed when a narrow second over 1400m at Orange. Has the upside to go one better. ALABAMA HUSSY (8) racing well and a win looks imminent. Comes out of a decent contest when second over 1300m at Canberra. Maps well and hard to stop. REVENUE RAISER (12) bounced off her good debut fifth at Beaumont (Newcastle), with a sound second over 1280m at Gilgandra. Expected to take a hand in the finish. VICIOUS RUMOUR (10) ticks a few boxes today and due for a change of luck. On the quick backup after sitting on the speed to run second over 1318m at Dubbo. Each way. THE BENTLEY (4) solid return when second at Gilgandra over the 1100m. Stays in the mix.
